      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STABLE TALK (4) kicked off his career in good style six days ago, beaten a nose into second over 1680m at Launceston. Finds a nice race and will take plenty of beating once more. LOTSEVEN (5) finished fourth on debut last time out when he broke in a 1680m event at Launceston six days ago. Beautifully placed and he should turn things around. ILLAWONG KAMISORI (1) is at the track for the first time. By Lather Up and hails from the R L Ashwood stable. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run. Trial winner who looks above average and looks well-placed to score at his first appearance. TIAMAT QUEEN (3) lines up for the first time. By Fear The Dragon and hails from the R L Ashwood stable. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run. Placed in a recent trial and is sure to prove very hard to beat.",
